      "date": "2026-03-15"
    },
    {
      "hash": "001ee31",
      "message": "fix: restore TodayTab card layout + fix TableMap horizontal scroll\n\nTodayTab was overwritten with a dashboard layout that removed card\nnavigation, timeclock portal, schedule view, and timesheet drill-downs.\nRestored the previous working version and added a compact inline\n\"Clocked In Now\" card showing active staff on the main view.\n\nTableMap: added overflow-hidden to prevent absolutely-positioned table\nbuttons from causing a horizontal scrollbar at 1024x768.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
      "branch": "fix/todaytab-regression-tablemap-scroll",
      "date": "2026-03-15"
    },
    {
