      "branch": "neil",
      "date": "2026-03-15"
    },
    {
      "hash": "cdde135",
      "message": "feat: add broadcast print mode for go-live testing\n\nAdds a \"Print to all printers (test mode)\" toggle in Settings > Device\nthat sends every kitchen ticket to ALL connected printers, bypassing\ncategory-based routing. Needed for Red Bar go-live test.\n\n- broadcastPrint field in DeviceSettings (localStorage, default OFF)\n- Toggle UI with amber warning banner when active\n- fireToKitchenPrinters() passes broadcast flag to API\n- fireOrder() local ESC/POS path respects broadcastPrint setting\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
      "branch": "feature/broadcast-print-mode",
      "date": "2026-03-15"
    },
    {
      "hash": "5eedf8f",
      "message": "fix(api): add scheduledStart/End, staffId, scheduledRole to shifts PATCH\n\nThe PATCH endpoint previously only handled status, actual times,\nhours, labor cost, notes, and station. Drag-drop shift reassignment\nin WeekGrid sends scheduledStart, scheduledEnd, staffId, and\nscheduledRole — these were silently ignored. Now all four fields\nare handled, so schedule edits persist to the database.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
      "branch": "fix/shifts-patch-endpoint",
      "date": "2026-03-15"
    },
    {
      "hash": "3b05784",
      "message": "fix(staff): bridge dual staff systems, wire real data, add Manage Staff panel\n\nStaffHome: resolveStaffId() now falls back to PwaUserContext user\nwhen staff-store has no matching PIN, fixing clock in/out failures\non fresh installs. Replaced hardcoded getTodayShifts()/getQuickStats()\nwith real data from timeclock-store and staff-store. Added break\nstart/end buttons. Owner/manager now see live \"Clocked In Now\" list\nwith elapsed times.\n\nNew ManageStaffPanel: full-screen modal with add/edit/remove staff,\nPIN validation (4-digit, uniqueness check), role selection, hourly\nrate. Accessible from StaffHome for owner/manager roles.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
      "branch": "fix/staff-features-audit",
      "date": "2026-03-15"
    },
